WizardLM-13b-v1.2 4_letter-number episode_0 request 54:
 ANSWER: 2009 

The numbers for all the letters are:

A: 7010
B: 9876
C: 8888
D: 7666
E: 5464
F: 7606
G: 4545
H: 9212
I: 4664
